
Cleric's Guild:  summon

Level  Command   Cost  Name

  3    vestment   50   Magical vestment: Armor
  4    hammer     50   Summon a magical hammer.
  5    servant    50   Unseen servant: A following bag.
       callservant 0   Call the servant back if lost.
  7    wthorn     20   Wall of thorns: Block exit. Caster may pass.
  10   blade      25   Blade barrier: Damages all monsters in room.
  13   wfire      30   Wall of fire: Shields you from attack.

